# 📋 Groq Migration - Quick Reference Guide

## 🎯 Migration Overview

```
FROM: Local Ollama LLM                  TO: Cloud Groq API
├─ Slowdown: GPU dependent             ├─ Faster: Cloud optimized
├─ No cost (CapEx)                      ├─ Usage-based pricing
├─ Local maintenance required           ├─ Fully managed
├─ Single GPU bottleneck                ├─ Scales automatically
└─ Full control                         └─ Less control needed

KEEPING: Upstash Vector (embeddings + storage)
├─ No changes to vector retrieval
├─ Same semantic search
└─ Better than local ChromaDB
```

---

## 🚀 5-Minute Quickstart

### 1️⃣ Get API Key
```
Go to: https://console.groq.com
→ Sign up/Login → API Keys → Copy key
```

### 2️⃣ Update .env
```ini
GROQ_API_KEY=gsk_your_key_here
GROQ_MODEL=llama-3.1-8b-instant
GROQ_TEMPERATURE=0.7
GROQ_MAX_TOKENS=1024
```

### 3️⃣ Install & Run
```bash
pip install groq
python groq_rag.py
```

