## 🔄 Architecture Flow

### Current (Ollama)
```
Question
   ↓
[Upstash Vector DB] ← Embeddings for question
   ↓ (retrieves 3 docs)
[Ollama LLM] ← Local GPU inference
   ↓
Answer
```

### New (Groq)
```
Question
   ↓
[Upstash Vector DB] ← Embeddings for question
   ↓ (retrieves 3 docs)
[Groq Cloud API] ← Cloud inference
   ↓
Answer
```

**Change**: Only LLM component moves to cloud

