## 🔍 Troubleshooting Matrix

| Problem | Solution | Command |
|---------|----------|---------|
| `GROQ_API_KEY missing` | Add to .env | `echo "GROQ_API_KEY=..." >> .env` |
| `Rate limit (429)` | Add delay | `time.sleep(1)` between queries |
| `Timeout` | Increase timeout | `GROQ_TIMEOUT=60` |
| `Empty response` | Check model | `GROQ_MODEL=llama-3.1-8b-instant` |
| `Connection error` | Check internet | `ping api.groq.com` |
| `Upstash failed` | Verify credentials | Check UPSTASH_VECTOR_* vars |

