## 💰 Cost Calculator

```
Assuming 1000 queries/day, avg 700 tokens per query:

Daily:    1,000 queries   × 700 tokens = 700K tokens
Monthly:  700K × 30 days = 21M tokens
Cost:     21M × $0.0005/1M = ~$10.50/month

Budget-conscious tips:
- Use lighter model for simple queries
- Enable caching (save 50% on repeat queries)
- Reduce context (top_k=1 vs top_k=3)
- Batch similar queries
```

