### Get Usage Stats
```python
from groq_rag import usage_tracker
import json

stats = usage_tracker.get_stats()
print(f"Cost so far: {stats['estimated_cost_usd']}")
print(f"Calls made: {stats['total_calls']}")
print(f"Success rate: {stats['successful_calls']}/{stats['total_calls']}")
```

### Manual Groq Call (No RAG)
```python
from groq_rag import groq_client

response = groq_client.chat.completions.create(
    model="llama-3.1-8b-instant",
    messages=[{"role": "user", "content": "Hello!"}]
)
print(response.choices[0].message.content)
```

