## 🚨 Error Messages Explained

| Error | Cause | Fix |
|-------|-------|-----|
| `RuntimeError: Missing GROQ_API_KEY` | .env not loaded | Add key to .env, restart |
| `RateLimitError: 429` | Too many requests | Add delay between queries |
| `APIConnectionError` | Network/firewall issue | Check connectivity, firewall |
| `ValueError: Unexpected response` | API format changed | Update code, check Groq docs |
| `FileNotFoundError: foods.json` | Data file missing | Verify JSON_FILE path |

